The Sims 3 Nude Patch (PC/Mac)

Instructions how to remove the nude censor in Sims 3

Copy Shaders_Win32.precomp

For Mac:
Rightclick on Sims file and choose Show Package Contents. Replace the file in /Contents/Resources/transgaming/c_drive/Program Files/Electronic Arts/The SIms 3/Game/Bin/

For PC:
Replace the file in C:Program FilesElectronic ArtsThe Sims 3GameBin
